title: Murdock Middle/High School
text:
Murdock Middle/High School (MMHS) is a public middle/high school located in <a href="Winchendon%2C%20Massachusetts">Winchendon</a>, <a href="Massachusetts">Massachusetts</a>. The current <a href="middle%20school">middle school</a> principal is Jessica L. Vezina, and the current <a href="Secondary%20school">high school</a> principal is Thad King. The superintendent is Joan Landers. The school implements the Summit Learning program for grades 6-8.
Athletics.
Murdock participates in a wide range of athletics, including <a href="Cheerleading">cheering</a>, <a href="American%20football">football</a>, <a href="Association%20football">soccer</a>, <a href="baseball">baseball</a>, <a href="softball">softball</a>, and <a href="basketball">basketball</a>.
